org.happy.artist.rmdmia.rcsm.providers.ros.client.message
Class TopicRegistryMessageDefinition

java.lang.Object
  org.happy.artist.rmdmia.rcsm.providers.ros.client.message.TopicRegistryMessageDefinition

public class TopicRegistryMessageDefinition
extends java.lang.Object

TopicRegistryMessageDefinition.java - The Topic Registry MessageDefinition, defines numeric variables associated with each TCPROS message Connection Header variable types. This class allows usage of the pre-existing movement processor registry format of #.#, that is a very simple, cheap property lookup algorithm. This registry message definition is for topic_registry.eax.
